{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"setEmails:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSArray","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSArray"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"emails","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Array of email address strings. Each must be a valid email format."}]}],"name":"emails"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Associates multiple email addresses with the current device for omnichannel","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"email campaigns. This is useful when users have multiple email addresses","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(work, personal, etc.) and want to receive communications on all of them."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"All provided emails will be linked to the same device and user ID,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"enabling unified targeting across all addresses."}]},{"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Register multiple emails from user profile:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["class UserProfileManager {","","    func syncEmailsFromProfile(_ profile: UserProfile) {","        var emails: [String] = []","","        if let primary = profile.primaryEmail {","            emails.append(primary)","        }","        if let secondary = profile.secondaryEmail {","            emails.append(secondary)","        }","        if let work = profile.workEmail {","            emails.append(work)","        }","","        guard !emails.isEmpty else { return }","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmails(emails)","","        \/\/ Update tags with email count","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"email_count\": emails.count,","            \"has_work_email\": profile.workEmail != nil,","            \"has_multiple_emails\": emails.count > 1","        ])","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setEmails:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setemails:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setEmails:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setEmails:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"setEmails:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"setEmails:"},"abstract":[{"text":"Registers multiple email addresses associated with the current user.","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"title":"PushwooshCore","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","abstract":[{"text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK.","type":"text"}],"role":"collection"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setEmails:":{"title":"setEmails:","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Registers multiple email addresses associated with the current user.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setEmails:"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setEmails:"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setEmails:","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setemails:"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"title":"PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"}}}